text: Evi Lanig (born 24 October 1933) is a German alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1952 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:German female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Germany Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:People from Oberallgäu
